        "subject": "LU-3000 tests: few fixes about DNE test-scripts",
        "message": "LU-3000 tests: few fixes about DNE test-scripts\n\n1. Since mds-survey does not support multiple MDT\ntests yet, so disable it for DNE.\n\n2. redirect error message to /dev/null, to avoid\ntoo much error message in the log, which might\nexplore the size of the log.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I63913fe94660e443fc86e7c005a2a82791e351ec\n"
      },
